PEOPLES
v.
SCHNEIDER 2018-1288 Supreme Court of Ohio. November 28, 2018

MERIT DECISION WITHOUT OPINION

On respondent's motion to dismiss. Motion granted. Cause dismissed. O'CONNOR, C.J., and O'DONNELL, KENNEDY, FISCHER, DEWINE, and DEGENARO, JJ., concur. FRENCH, J., not participating.
